component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4f436ad2-b222-4b84-99e0-224bfb3dc187\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-3b94ee05-b234-42fb-8fed-ed8f3e0a8011\">자신도 모르게 허리를 숙인 채로 걷는 경험, 혹시 있으신가요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d042b621-425d-49fb-9c81-c624f535852e\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-9fdf7d65-95bf-4ebf-9543-f83c59f95b43\">그런 경우에는</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-8ef4727f-405e-413c-b3f8-f3d6d744e4b1\"><b> 척추관 협착증</b></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-44ac9287-b2b8-49f8-a105-c6bd6bd47848\">을 의심해볼 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-34c7c386-7f14-4d72-9eff-f4391c0108fe\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-8050c49e-19d9-42ae-a5ea-8006b81b0714\">.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fb26cf85-ea85-4f6f-87cb-df253ff2b5ff\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-f067097a-e812-4b6a-aee2-adca07b86cd8\">척추관이 좁아지면서 신경이 눌려 통증이 발생하는 증상으로,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d3a3c0ec-6764-433a-85fd-581d95e9cd1f\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" 